        "text": "# \ud83d\udfe2 HEARTBEAT_WAKEUP\nYou have been routed ONE isolated task. \n*Task ID*: EPIC-DFP\n*Module*: SYSTEM\n*Workdir*: /home/ienliven/Projects/sdlc-factory/workspace/EPIC-DFP\n*Phase*: ARCHITECTURE\n\n## SYSTEM CONTEXT\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"module_id\": \"SYSTEM\",\n  \"regression_context\": \"No active regression reported.\",\n  \"structural_context\": \"No structural boundaries found (API_CONTRACTS.md missing or module not defined).\",\n  \"semantic_context\": \"No legacy semantic snippet queries found for this module.\",\n  \"memory_insights\": \"No historic pgvector insights found for architect.\"\n}\n```\n\nThe SDLC Protocol and your Playbook are your core instructions.\nCRITICAL: If successful, your handoff JSON must strictly validate against this schema:\n```json\n{\n  \"oneOf\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"required\": [\n        \"status\",\n        \"phase_completed\",\n        \"api_contracts_hash\",\n        \"vertical_slices\"\n      ],\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"status\": {\n          \"const\": \"success\"\n        },\n        \"phase_completed\": {\n          \"const\": \"ARCHITECTURE\"\n        },\n        \"api_contracts_hash\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"vertical_slices\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"items\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"required\": [\n              \"module_name\",\n              \"assigned_agent\"\n            ],\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"module_name\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              },\n              \"assigned_agent\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              },\n              \"context_queries\": {\n                \"type\": \"array\",\n                \"items\": {\n                  \"type\": \"string\"\n                }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"obje