        "thought_signature": "CqkFAY89a197fBzPh8l96QFM3Lb1OQyb6VT0eGNrSh2m-v6E5pVd9EMAkXAIInAGNYpbipa6zmCiJ547ykSux85xKH_tkwapXrAtsQOopTK8oudXD5wdW4DD4fM7f6h2sIwNH24dGg4C55IGnqbEX2Ii_O_pMIBmjwOeRNDZhLJMaCGhZ_7-ApO7OHG8QxWb-BVB2iphL9npkMX_6vi1dJxeAx35cdGcg-BxmzNJO4uRIdTVPXZ1nTn9e1N5m3Aimldi2CsFU83NiG6rtiGkoO-rEJBRWWxKtm6QMglVvAxvgXciXDNvzkaUFUYCAy06qZiL_YEykWVNi3R0srmvyaf0dC_0qXnXsgdRKXUKtKe-p9tcn3dUMGJgxrAeX96wsKBkVCdY45OOwDLUJuNZt5fJTZCL1lbBQhd5PiNqdDThlYi70vnlzyu6B2Cx-qNH2I7P6KjHr4Du50m1-VIMfngcXnvNWWiJYcRIpx64r5wx5pHocvGYP0ti2VT4rHjRdYvtrOmmxCRQT4gdoFOtadW5ApmHHYhRiphhXBIn_M79aeHuzt5YKgpU_4sxKsOqBBpg3X_6cH0nCQH15RyBUaKorBPBbAFgkMlmxk8SANWcNSXqorG4JjMvBhGa9x8qaysX8-WEYshbTLAx50pnrp2t5wUJOsJKBugpV14FQwUXPqUAOzZTDFK7M_Q5E-bXQrZnoLlFwKkI93Z4hvMOt93Tw0WTSqLRBmJ-PB4OL7_qjKSKSZLb-IrEuZdKc710DkKfiwPd3RF7ke0r4g83hwGPh28PNV0b_DvGEgihYgcJ6fNXPXVMJbwKgjjzeLEdReWXXKMOXCU3aMmYJOpwIP-OfnqPxfMvMXZkidyuuu7WmPnB_xEJxruaEQZWb9s7fo8o2UuoAzSzzeaT",
