        "function_call": null,
        "function_response": null,
        "inline_data": null,
        "text": "I have successfully analyzed the product specification and generated the architectural contracts for the Dimensional Factor Pulse (DFP) system. \n\nThe architecture has been decomposed into three vertical slices:\n1. **`ui-gateway` (ORCHESTRATOR)**: Responsible for the React/Vite frontend, Nginx reverse proxy, and the global `docker-compose.yml` orchestration.\n2. **`logic-api` (LEAF)**: A Python/FastAPI backend that handles data fetching via `yfinance`, premium calculations, and database interactions with explicit connection polling.\n3. **`data-store` (LEAF)**: A PostgreSQL database module responsible for schema initialization via `init.sql`.\n\nThe `docs/API_CONTRACTS.md` and `handoff/arch_payload.json` have been written, and the state has been advanced to `AWAITING_MODULES` to spawn the child tasks.",
